column5: Managed to get one last largemouth for the season, 2 3/4 lbs. Kinda funny though. Just got to that spot and 2 other guys were on the other side fishing getting nuthin' and I go in the other and pluck this baby out. Should've seen the look on their faces.
Nice one Stern Rules Got to love it when you can hook one right off the bat!!! Thanks for sharing Leechman
First cast and got nothing after that. Got snagged twice so gave up but better than nothing.
wtg... we went out today and got skunked for bass... one of our guys, Chris K from here, got a nice pike though
Nice to catch 1 right out from under some one else, It's been awhile since I caught a Large Mouth Richard
A large mouth!!!!  you must be some type of master or something.  they were dead off 2 months ago here couldnt get anything to hit!

Gotta love that feeling tho , especially when you're stuck on shore and they're in a boat   heh  Congrats on the catch, I can admit that it definitely ain't getting easier catchin these bucketmouths in these almost freezing conditions, but we sure love to try  Great end to the season, thanks for sharing  -fishindude
Beauty, nice job man.  kudos, MTBF
Were you trying to copy the look on their faces in the photo?    Nice fish, man!
